Roosa Funmilayo Ariyo (amụrụ na 13 June 1994) bụ onye na-agba bọọlụ na Naijiría nke a mụrụ na Finland nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-aga n'ihu maka otu Belgian Club YLA na otu ụmụ nwanyị nke Naijiria.
A zụlitere Ariyo na Helsinki na Espoo. Nna ya bụ onye Naijirịa na nne ya bụ onye Finland.
Ariyo gara Monroe Community College na Mahadum Bridgeport na United States.
Ariyo agbaala bọọlụ maka FC Honka na Tikkurilan Palloseura na Finland na Jitex BK na Sweden.
Ariyo mere nke mbụ ya na Naịjirịa na 10 June 2021 na mmeri enyi na enyi na Jamaica.
